     <div type="notice_regarding_errata">
   <pb facs="722"/>
   <head>An Aduertisement.</head>
   <p>
      <hi>WHereas in the former edition this page was stuffed full of Errata, which were occasioned by reason of the various matter and words vsed in this Historie, not common obvious in other Authors; such care in this second Edition hath beene taken, as that they haue all beene amended, whereby the Readers paines to mend, or be offended with them, is taken away. This I thought good to giue notice of, least any should thinke them omitted, not amended.</hi>
   </p>
